    "causal_summary": "The Spec Kit Memory graph has 3,854 causal edges at 79.92% coverage but is underutilized: `memory_search(\"Semantic Search\")` returns 0 results, graph signals are invisible to users, and the graph fires only reactively via causal boost. Phase 007 surveyed 7 external graph memory systems and produced a 12-item ranked improvement backlog. This spec implements the top 8 improvements across 4 dependency-ordered phases.",
